Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay focused, focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to those around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Be like the blue sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am... I'm his homeroom teacher, Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Principal...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:29.50,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculously, he got off with only a bone\Nfracture to his foot and some cracked ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we should be happy his life was saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What about regaining consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "He jumped?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They were playing around on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...when they started talking about whether they could jump to the roof of the connecting passageway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazhuhiko-kun said he could make it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he fell without reaching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kazuhiko tell you this himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They are a close bunch who are always joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this was some horseplay that went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.48,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Horseplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly regret that it turned into a tragic accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are all of your apologies?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.29,Double Line,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,About the treatment costs, \Nbecause the school's insurance will cover it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.69,0:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...well, we should be amicable about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't you lose to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.76,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It's Kazuhiko-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lose to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at school will be waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna eat some ramen on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez. Don't say stupid things.\NYou guys head straight on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were being bullied, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes are filled with an anger\Npowerful enough to make you shiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the same time, they are also filled with grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This illustration of Acala, handed down to the \NDairokuteru Temple is an unquestioned masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But the colors have weakened so much so over the years that everyone in the region has been grieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma K?kichi-san was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that reason, \Nhe volunteered to restore this painting for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He has the skills needed to win\Nthe Itabashi Art Contest three times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And the results of his work were this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether this is seen as having been ruined by graffiti...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...or as having just slightly strayed from being\Na restoration will differ upon the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,However, please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma-san is still in the middle of his restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Chief Priest doesn't force him to end it\Nand if he could continue with his repairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...a dramatic change will appear; \None as if the original Acala itself had been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Tanuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget this could be said to be an act of good will by an artist of the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Defendant will hereby pay the Plaintiff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:12.93,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,290)}Ruling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...50 million yen ($500,000)...{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and will pay the money over five yearly installments beginning on November 20, 2012...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...and continuing until such payments are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Main Clause 2: the Defendant's legal costs will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.17,Double Line,,0,0,0,,He'll be sarcastic with me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,3: This ruling will be enforced as much as possible during the first term.
