Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.12,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\shad1\blur1\fnPresent\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H4C4C4C&\fs40\b0\pos(477.775,392.089)}French Alps Region
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318.806,396.766)}Are you okay, Monsieur?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I used to do cross-country skiing long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...seems I've gotten myself into an embarrassing situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.21,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, him... That person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321.508,390.669)}The "Matterhorn" is magnificent today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.\NYou're accompanying this man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have hurt his hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this person here helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, I don't know who on earth you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...but my heart won't let me settle this\Nwith a mere offering of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That hill's ski jump was shut down just now\Nand since I'm bored at the hotel I'm staying at...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...please allow me to entertain you at my hotel with the Chef's Special Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With a foie gras, cheese fondue, \Na spectacular Brassica campestris and the finest crepes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Hattori-san, don't go absentminded on me\Nand take off these skis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.86,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Um, what about your hip?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mayuzumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please put that on Do-not-disturb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude of her.\NCome, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go to Hakuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the Komikado Law Firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.22,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\bord1\blur1\i1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(325.664,395.326)\fs32}2 Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The swelling in my foot, which you stamped on last night,\Nhasn't gone down and is still in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of demanding consolation money\Nand filing a criminal complaint for bodily injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a legitimate act of self defense\Nagainst being forced into an indecent act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I may also file a criminal complaint against you for attempted rape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You came up to my room two days in a row\Nand guzzled down four bottles of my Chateau Margaux...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I don't think such a silly story would be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say it won't be accepted,\Nshall we try fighting it out in court?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting. You don't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.30,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I do know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a misunderstanding jerk who thinks he can get anything he wants with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are a misunderstanding woman who doesn't have the eyes to recognize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...who's a first-class man when she's out man-hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so much of your beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If you asked me, your face gets 65 points, your body 40 while that personality of yours is outside the range!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(321.508,392.678)}Aie, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ala!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the same spot again... I'll sue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make a switch over to an elegant French Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonjour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was praying it was just a similar-looking bow-legged French woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I couldn't reach you by phone,\NI came out directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to Japan. We have a request for services we absolutely have to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!\NWhat's more, you're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A middle school bullying problem, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun is still in a coma and it isn't known when he will regain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But the school is trying to sweep it under the rug by calling it a freak accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As ever, you only bring in disease-laden germs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The one being bullied is the one with the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to hide the problem, the ones who are bullied are being isolated to protect the ones doing the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a deep-rooted darkness of Japanese education.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, this asadora heroine is racing along at full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely loathe brats and schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If they really want me to do this, then 10 million yen in cash...\N No, make that 20 million yen! ($200,000)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The client's husband died early and she works part-time for a bento provider, so it's just her and her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What I hate even more than brats and schools are poor people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...the joy that comes from helping someone who is suffering can't be counted in money...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.36,Double Line,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi-sensei, is there no choice but for you to handle it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I want to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating...\Nbut I'm not sure I could win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A 120% chance you can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to France and bowed my head to the one I hate, Sensei! Please do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't! I won't!\NI'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This place isn't all that much different from Habuka-mura in Nagano!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this like Habuka-mura!? It's totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.68,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It is Hakuba. Wherever you look, it's Hakuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,SHUT UP!\NMy attorney's fee will be 20 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell those poor people who can't afford it that they will just have to give up and commit double suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...along with you, their block-headed lawyer, by blowing yourselves to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.52,Double Line,,0,0,0,,This hand won't accept that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget you already owe me a ton of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a casino nearby, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.63,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you teach me how to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was once a dealer in Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Baccarat is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.33,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, moooooronl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, Hattori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Better yet, let's offer ourselves to the school as a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We might be able to make quite a haul from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only able to earn 153,600 euros.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japanese yen, that is 18,124,030 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be the greatest amount of winnings from that casino ever since it began.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never seen a person with such a talent at gambling before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. The remainder will just have to come from Hidemi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up with a plan to make use of this talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Komikado-sensei, let's go back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And be reborn as the lawyer who's an ally of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san, please bury this person in the perpetual snows of the Matterhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Objection! Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:05.84,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(123.716,447.775)}Sakai Masato
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.88,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(520.136,447.41)}Aragaki Yui
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.58,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(161.562,445.204)}Namase Katsuhsia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:13.62,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(99.385,450.252)}Koike Eiko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.65,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465.59,448.829)}Taguchi Junnosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.69,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(508.84,449.878)}Yano Masato
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.22,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(136.083,448.156)}Satomi Kotaro
