Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:29.00,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2DD9D6&\fnImpact\fs92\frz2.811\i1\pos(277.118,100.854)}Legal High Special
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazu-kun, the lawyer has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he'll take this to court for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Komikado-sensei. \NHe's a lawyer who's never been defeated in court even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely take on your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I think it could be called a cracked bone,\Ncould you try touching it for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! With a little more gentleness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, stronger.\NYes... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take Kazuhiko-kun's hand and talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass on that.\NWe don't know if he could even hear my talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've decided I won't be holding hands\Nwith any middle school boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you say Kazuhiko-kun has been bullied at school; \Nis that something you can prove?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Because he won't tell me anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.59,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, what evidence to you have that he was bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun has had a fear of heights ever since he was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...so much so that he isn't even able to cross pedestrian foot bridges.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So he simply wouldn't be able to do something as idiotic as jump off a roof as part of a practical joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle school boys are mostly idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful with the words you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be assuming too much.{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...I do feel I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We will immediately submit a lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be suing the city that established the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...as well as the parents of the boys who were the perpetrators.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No. We'll drop the perpetrators and their parents and wring the school out instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? The theory is that a lawsuit against the three parties involved is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:11.48,Double Line,,0,0,0,,What do you know about theory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's add in a little mental consolation money of ten million yen for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You could buy out that bento shop you work\Npart-time at and become its owner if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll pray for your son's recovery to full health.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Kazuhiko-kun will surely recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.02,Double Line,,0,0,0,,If he recovers, then we lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A bullying trial is far and away more difficult than your insufficient brain capacity could ever imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I performed a rigorous investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:58.71,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\frz21.25\fs24\c&H444444&\move(353.982,215.191,346.8,149.204,27,2964)}Lawsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:14:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...and was unable to find any evidence of bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This bullying case is truly like a bolt from the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to settle this amicably somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, that would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The opponent lawyer is a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...who happily sows wildfires by burning gasoline in places where they have no fires or smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do but fight this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He is no rival for our Miki Choichiro-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows all there is about Komikado-sensei's skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How many wins and how many losses\Nhave you had against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How many wins and how many losses have I had against Komikado-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say we've lost all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we almost win one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.99,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I have no memory of any wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, in bullying lawsuits such as these...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...the first thing to keep in mind is\Nit is very unlikely the school will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's kick this around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who will you put in charge of this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well-suited for it.\NBecause I'm young and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have that newcomer take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The rookie we have high hopes for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.89,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It'd be good experience for him, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be what you say, but this is way over the head of a first year like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working under Sensei for far longer\Nand have piled up some experience in my career.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now I can defeat Komikado-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.44,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Shall we have Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since we last had sushi, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Ito, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Ide."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.37,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.79,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\frz345.1\pos(320,219.778)}Do you feel there is bullying going on at this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Vague answers to vague questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:18.23,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\fay0.2\an4\c&H1F1739&\3c&H7D97A3&\frz31.63\pos(78.524,242.887)}Feel you may have seen it\NMay have seen it\NFeel you may not have seen it\NMay have seen it, but could be wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It could easily be said that this\Nfact-finding survey was sloppily done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A school isn't for students, it's for teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only obvious they would protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for coming while you're eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll be together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like the only law offices in this country\Nare mine and yours, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's said that's because there are no lawyers out there who want to give you the time of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Having just become a fresh new lawyer,\Nwe have brought in an innocent newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're putting a first-year rookie in charge of this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you've run out of talent and now have to turn to acne-faced boys to be your aces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, isn't this a pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That in their debut battle, \Nwith no hope of success against a world champion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the rookie lawyer, Teshigawara Isao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A pheasant. I shot it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU shot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In Chichibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a trifling hobby of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... this is an excellent bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the bullet is still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sixth bullet, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you do this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:29.16,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...I used to hunt in Alaska.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We will have pot pheasant today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Komikado-sensei, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a great deal about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,By holding their hand, \Nyou can gain a rough idea about a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei's hand is... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's similar to Mick Jagger's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mick Jagger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, I invited him to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Teshigawara-sensei has managed many companies up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and is a man who has helped in the success of many businesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown tired of making money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Resolving to giving himself a new challenge before he leaves his 60s...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...it seems he passed the bar exam on his first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was just good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Komikado-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being a lawyer is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no newcomers or veterans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When they stand up in court,\Nthey are all just private soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm excited right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care to watch your blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss this without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The school wishes for a settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They will do all in their power\Nto maximize the settlement money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the phrase, \N"as a result of bullying," must not be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this attitude from the school's side that Hidemi-san finds unforgivable and why she filed this lawsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A very energetic young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:17:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be gentle with your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mayuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:00.89,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This hand, if I recall... Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Madonna or was it Britney?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't quite remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be Madonna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Teshigawara-sensei. \NThere is just one word I have to say at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It is thirty years too soon for you to be making settlement negotiations with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty years?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... That's a long time to have to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if you'd like, I will be providing lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, we've obliged on you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.49,Double Line,,0,0,0,,We'll see you in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, I think as a rookie I may bring you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you very much for your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying that the gap in atmosphere you two exude is something frightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The bar exam should come with an age limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However you look at it, he seems more like the veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, though well past 60, he's still just\Na glittery first year schoolboy with satchel in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can beat him hands down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After speaking to the secretary, it seems the\NPresiding Judge is also a newly-appointed person as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Beppu Toshiko, a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more convienient. Women judges tend to be sympathetic towards bullied children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be a slam dunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.20,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, court is in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.97,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,290)\fs48}First Round, Oral Arguments
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun is fighting hard for his life today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:20:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The one solely responsible for causing such a tragedy is this school, which tolerated the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is case of extortion as well as bodily injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it wouldn't be an exaggeration to call it attempted murder as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.75,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Presiding Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Attorney for the Defendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is simply to confirm the substance of the lawsuit, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Plaintiff's attorney has already begun making statements of opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Attorney for the Plaintiff, please refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Presiding Judge, I want you to recognize the importance of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:30.80,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Please refrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This case is now about the bullying that is occurring in schools throughout Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.08,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Please refrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a tendency of the Plaintiff's attorney...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...to unnecessarily use sensationalistic words out of mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think that is a very dangerous technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.88,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado Kensuke-sensei, your attitude in court seems a little too "as you please."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Other judges may have permitted you this,\Nbut I will NOT allow it in my court.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You will rigidly adhere to the rules and morals of this court.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Court is adjourned for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really pissed off, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I talk well and fluently. Judge that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Call for our ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru-kun, bury yourself deeply into that rabbit middle school. I want you to collect info.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I value your enthusiasm, but going in as a transfer student just isn't going to work, now is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A temporary coach for the soccer club?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can only leg-lift a ball twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this time around it'll be impossible for you to just to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The security at the school has been tightened up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.85,Double Line,,0,0,0,,You don't! This isn't play time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, proving this was bullying will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones doing the bullying may not even be aware they're doing it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, \Nthere may have been times when I was bullied, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is why Sensei has such a bad character\Nbecause you were bullied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't. Anyone who tried to bully me understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...I would have re-payed them 500 times over for it with my own hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Brandishing your righteousness around...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...you would have been the obnoxious class rep who became an easy target for bullying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I was fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, if I'm forced to say it,\NI did have natto put into my indoor shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:17.13,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(12.333,12.444)}Natto: fermented soybeans
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.13,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...and if I sat down in a chair it would often have had superglue put on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...and there was a time during the school excursion when everyone hid out and I ended up visiting Kyoto alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You were hit with an insane amount of bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That was bullying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:27.99,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so I WAS bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it five years ago... Me and some friends\Ncornered this fellow up on Taisetsuzan-kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting up wind... Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed it in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.27,0:22:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what I want for this trial as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado-sensei will use all sorts of means to get into the school to gain information.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have arranged with the school to strengthen their security.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...no matter how much security you have, \Nwon't it be impossible to guard all of the students?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:05.59,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we invite him in, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Invite him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt our rival would just obtain even more cards to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.83,0:23:12.79,Double Line,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We will fully monitor whatever cards he does pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, if it's that school, it should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite daring of our enemy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna head back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around! Every one of them are wearing the same cheap jerseys...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and are being forced into\Ncollective behavior just like in a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And earlier there was a girl who had a jersey on under her skirt while wearing a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.56,0:23:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.43,0:23:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to us where you go or with whom you talk.{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.27,0:23:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, thanks for your hard work. \NPlease sit over here. We'll bring you tea right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Teruko-sensei, make it hot, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.66,0:24:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... This truly was a tragic event.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We absolutely won't let anyone go up on the roof any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.54,0:24:16.41,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Kogure will definitely recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.37,0:24:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know if there was bullying involved, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.89,0:24:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have such a thing going on here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Year two, Class C has P.E. while in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys have basketball while the girls have volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.85,0:24:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Would you like to work up a sweat along with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:34.75,Double Line,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, oi, oi, oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.99,0:24:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shorten the distance between you and the students, they'll be easier to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.22,0:24:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more point!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.32,0:24:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take my play lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.84,0:25:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, swift attack! Now, I'm open! I'm open here! I'm open here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.97,0:25:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm always open...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.12,0:25:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.61,0:25:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.67,0:25:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.00,0:25:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow this brings back\Nbittersweet feelings, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.90,0:25:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I only recall the smell of the rag which had wiped up the milk someone had vomited.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.24,0:25:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah hello, I'm the homeroom teacher for this class, Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.04,0:25:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you. \NWe're the lawyers Mayuzumi and Komikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.19,0:25:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, today is "Give me Wings," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.63,0:25:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.63,0:25:46.19,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.48,0:25:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, because part of what I do is be the adviser for the Chorus Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.11,0:25:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...it is the custom of my class when they return to their homeroom activities to sing as a chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.04,0:25:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.50,0:25:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, come sing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.70,0:25:59.35,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes! Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.28,0:25:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! We definitely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.55,0:26:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a strategy to become more intimate with the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.37,0:26:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a strategy to destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.80,0:26:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.97,0:26:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.75,0:26:34.67,singing,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\}Ima watashi no negai goto ga\N{\fs37\}What I wish for right now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.88,0:26:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you sang really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.51,0:26:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi-san, you were the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.67,0:26:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you were the best! After all, a chorus isn't made up of just one person!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.13,0:26:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It was a great success, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.24,0:26:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, before your class activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.83,0:27:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...it seems the lawyers need to talk to all of you,\Nso give them some of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.16,0:27:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.37,0:27:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Machiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.68,0:27:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.59,0:27:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh... I am the lawyer, Mayuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.45,0:27:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... All of you know that the matter of Kogure-kun being injured is going to trial, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.85,0:27:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... well... Because this may be a place where\Nit would be hard for you to talk about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.01,0:27:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...please tell us your stories later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.27,0:27:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't feel reserved.\NPlease ask all that you want here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.83,0:27:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is a class where we exchange views about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.24,0:27:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Still it's best to do that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.39,0:27:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,May I distribute my business card?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.95,0:27:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.44,0:27:46.01,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur2\an4\fs22\2c&H516B76&\3c&H516A76&\pos(270.462,147.406)\frz30.7}Komikado Law Offices\N Lawyer\NMayuzumi Machiko
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.01,0:27:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have anything you'd like to tell or ask me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.80,0:27:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...please contact me at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.41,0:27:54.75,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.3\blur2\bord3\c&H21333B&\3c&H4E6878&\b1\frz16.05\frx2\fry344\pos(200.949,246.386)}School Motto\N\NFriendship\N\NHarmony\N\NPhilanthropy
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.65,0:27:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Because this is a rare opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.95,0:28:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...could we ask you the favor of giving us a special class lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.23,0:28:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I couldn't give a lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.66,0:28:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I? Then, I guess there's nothing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.21,0:28:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.60,0:28:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,From me there is just one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.05,0:28:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, the one thing I want you to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.88,0:28:36.36,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5B696C&\pos(199.351,101.641)}people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.59,0:28:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The character for "people" is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.25,0:28:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That people should support one other...\NIt doesn't mean that!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.23,0:28:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the hieroglyphic of a single human being standing on the earth with their legs apart like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.10,0:28:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We are born alone, we live alone and we die alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.56,0:28:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The friends and relationships you make during your middle school years...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.58,0:28:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be mostly useless during your life going forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, they'll be worthless;\Ntying yourselves to local friendships and loves...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.13,0:29:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...becomes a rotten chain inhibiting the freedom of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.96,0:29:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dare to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.42,0:29:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This class is shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.71,0:29:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is nothing but a box of oranges and the oranges are rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.25,0:29:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being in this room should make you want to vomit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.28,0:29:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And so without reserve, because you've heard what kind of place this is, I'll rely upon your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.63,0:29:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama Shun...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.51,0:29:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...Takagi Kento...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.34,0:29:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sasaoka Kosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.19,0:29:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kanamori Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they force Kogure Kazuhiko off of the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.76,0:29:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of bullying was he undergoing on a routine basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, the way you put that...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.12,0:29:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We sued this school, but we didn't file one against you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.65,0:29:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our compassion for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.16,0:29:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, since you won't be punished,\Nit won't be necessary for you guys to pay reparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.83,0:29:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't hesitate to tell us the truth.\NHowever...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.55,0:29:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you lie or keep any secrets from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.78,0:29:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll turn you into defendants right this minute\Nand do everything in my power to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.11,0:29:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.03,0:29:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it won't only be you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.56,0:29:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going around to each of the companies your Fathers are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.09,0:30:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going to your Mothers' neighborhood associations. \NAnd to all your friends as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.17,0:30:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.28,0:30:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.13,0:30:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's certain Aoyama-kun and the others went too far in their mischievousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.57,0:30:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But these children have roots of love for their friends that reach down deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.40,0:30:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They actively reached out to\Nthe withdrawn Kogure-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.68,0:30:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...and told him he shouldn't keep to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.68,0:30:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Aoyama-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.23,0:30:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko and I are best buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.69,0:30:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He himself jumped from that roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.41,0:30:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...saying he could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.25,0:30:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have stopped him...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.47,0:30:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think everyone in this class feels the same way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.60,0:30:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun is their precious friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.14,0:30:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...both now...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.22,0:30:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...and in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.25,0:31:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and sing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.57,0:31:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That Fujii-sensei is a wonderful teacher, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.48,0:31:08.32,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Far too wonderful; she makes me vomit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.32,0:31:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you don't like about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.81,0:31:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that artificial smile of hers\Nand the way she speaks like some music star!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.79,0:31:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally turned that class into some Fairyland due to the half-hearted atmosphere she creates.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.52,0:31:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fairyland?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.40,0:31:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That hypocritical, fake Julie Andrews smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.43,0:31:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...along with her {\i1}"All of you are being brainwashed"{\i0} singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.67,0:31:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Brainwashed" is exaggerating things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.13,0:31:33.26,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.26,0:31:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though this situation has occurred, not a single one of them looks as if they care about the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.92,0:31:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them were singing those songs with bright smiles on their faces. Don't you think that's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.79,0:31:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I've begun feeling confused by this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.07,0:31:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether there really was any bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.41,0:31:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there wasn't any bullying going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.91,0:31:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!\NThis is the brainwashing I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.69,0:31:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the mutton taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:52.49,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.57,0:31:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, mutton!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.77,0:31:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in that class are sheep being kept by her.\NAnd today, you became just one more of her sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.53,0:32:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really not so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.34,0:32:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were lying, it sure didn't look like it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.83,0:32:05.13,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.13,0:32:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all expressing their true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.27,0:32:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the difficulty that comes along with a bullying trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.10,0:32:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as you weren't able to harvest anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.56,0:32:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll need to reconsider your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.57,0:32:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san, who said there wasn't a harvest?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.00,0:32:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.72,0:32:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get something?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.67,0:32:21.50,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Of course. What's more, without the enemy even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.35,0:32:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The speakers aren't broken.\NThat's what her voice sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.57,0:32:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this will just rot our ears, let's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.97,0:32:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All the information the enemy got is manageable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.21,0:32:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Teshigahara-sensei expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.50,0:32:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.64,0:32:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...allowing them prance around in your territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.59,0:32:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.40,0:32:59.32,Double Line,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.32,0:33:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to zoom in on that guy's hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.93,0:33:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.72,0:33:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.53,0:33:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely his contact information and some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.55,0:33:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.43,0:33:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Clever, isn't he...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.30,0:33:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.60,0:33:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems there was a spot where you witnessed Kogure-kun being bullied many times over, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.78,0:33:23.75,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.98,0:33:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They surrounded him, kicked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and hit him with stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.70,0:33:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How did Kogure-kun appear during this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.00,0:33:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He cried out for them to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.79,0:33:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure-kun said it over and over,\Nbut that just escalated their laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.06,0:33:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he was enjoying it himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.75,0:33:44.05,Double Line,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.65,0:33:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That was bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.05,0:33:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.21,0:33:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.57,0:33:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.53,0:33:54.33,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.33,0:33:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kogure Kazuhiko-kun you say encountered this bullying is which one of the children shown here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.27,0:34:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.18,0:34:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.89,0:34:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure Kazuhiko-kun isn't among these.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.79,0:34:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.24,0:34:13.23,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.12,0:34:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.23,0:34:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, which are the children you say were doing the bullying?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.86,0:34:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.08,0:34:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't in here, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.55,0:34:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This child and this child and this child and this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.65,0:34:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.64,0:34:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my intention to blame your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.40,0:34:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand how you feel all too well myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.69,0:34:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When you reach our age, even when watching TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.18,0:34:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...all the young men nowadays look the same, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.68,0:34:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.59,0:34:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking honestly, because of my age...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.04,0:34:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't tell who's who among each of the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.76,0:35:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I spoke carelessly before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.91,0:35:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.41,0:35:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Formidable, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:09.90,Double Line,,0,0,0,,He has to be or it wouldn't be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.49,0:35:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a guerrilla war.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.08,0:35:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.59,0:35:19.96,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(301.623,92.062)}U Middle School's Vicious Bullying
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.96,0:35:22.96,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376.729,144.213)\frz342.7}Trial for Extortion to Jump off Roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.50,0:35:28.24,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2B0A55&\fs48\pos(295.231,150.599)}Boy Victim Still Unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.64,0:35:31.57,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H281850&\fs48\pos(318.402,134.634)\frz359}Bullying at U city's U Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.57,0:35:32.41,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\an4\pos(125.044,318.759)\c&H39205C&\frz358.4}Boy Victim Still Unconscious\N\NBullying at U city's U Middle School\N
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.84,0:35:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.84,0:35:38.58,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur2\fs22\c&H514FA5&\3c&HB87F60&\move(411.879,92.73,391.182,91.666,27,2730)}Walking with Friends\N{\c&H000000&}Usagi-gaoka \NMiddle School
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.99,0:35:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.27,0:35:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-san, 'morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.95,0:35:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be "Fujii-sensei, good morning," shouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Kaori, you're painting your cheeks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.13,0:35:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Please overlook it. I'm covering up my acne.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.47,0:35:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you should use more skill in applying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.04,0:35:51.10,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.72,0:35:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what is this? Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.29,0:35:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,, You haven't seen any bullying going on at this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.23,0:35:58.94,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.94,0:36:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.20,0:36:01.51,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Do you have permission for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.51,0:36:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're preventing us from knowing what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.40,0:36:05.23,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.93,0:36:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be Fujii-sensei of Year Two, Class C?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.71,0:36:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.60,0:36:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.83,0:36:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the homeroom teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.55,0:36:15.03,Double Line,,0,0,0,, Hey, there's a lot of things we want to ask, \Nso would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.03,0:36:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! Please stop it with those cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.87,0:36:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta the way, outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.80,0:36:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk with the Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.99,0:36:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.65,0:36:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.13,0:36:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to ask about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:28.40,Boxed,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\3c&H2B302B&\frz11.1\pos(217.728,156.032)}2 Boys of U City, U Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:28.40,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\3c&HA2AEAC&\b1\fs48\c&H2D302D&\frz11.25\pos(349.563,224.146)}"Bullying Into a Fall"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:28.40,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&H9DAAA6&\3c&H2B2C29&\b1\fs48\frz11.08\pos(334.382,330.576)}Student Victim Still Unconscious
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.10,0:36:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you open an explanation meeting for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.40,0:36:29.90,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HC6D6D6&\fs18\pos(228.115,406.142)\frz359}U City Superintendent\h\h\hHomeroom Teacher and Principal (upper right)
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.22,0:36:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We were unable to hold classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.38,0:36:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guardians who didn't want their children attending school took them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.10,0:36:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos of the students and teachers are swirling around on the Internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.92,0:36:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something that should not be!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.92,0:37:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's calm down. Miki-sensei told you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.61,0:37:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That the opposing lawyer would set wildfires.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.73,0:37:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemy works by throwing things into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.02,0:37:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say this to the teachers and students.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.97,0:37:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't worry about anything."\N"We of Usagi-gaoka Middle School are splendid."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.10,0:37:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.96,0:37:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it is for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.96,0:37:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The tone of the press will change before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.47,0:37:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one you need be careful about is their homeroom teacher, Fujii-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.87,0:37:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the card the enemy wants most.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's strengthen our guard around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.91,0:37:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What we want isn't just to defend, but to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.10,0:37:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you have at hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.64,0:37:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not without something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.97,0:37:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we do some chumming and see if anything bites?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.89,0:38:05.19,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fs58\b1\frz60.57\move(33.958,378.359,86.365,227.228,25,1293)}Quit
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.19,0:38:06.13,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur2\pos(172.185,198.492)\frz14.61\3c&H434134&\b1}Crap Woman\NCriminal
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.13,0:38:07.06,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur3\3c&H3E392C&\frz22\move(288.839,168.692,315.836,34.59,21,921)}You should jump, too
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.06,0:38:07.66,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.2\3c&H383125&\fs72\pos(333.499,110.155)\frz356.5\b1\c&H240B0C&}You should be fired
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.15,0:38:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My sympathies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.74,0:38:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.07,0:38:17.77,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the students, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.41,0:38:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This harrassment seems to be going on at the homes of Aoyama and the others as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.02,0:38:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who brought on this situation was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.87,0:38:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one who can end it again is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.63,0:38:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you admit to the existence of bullying, \Nthen the responsibilty the school side holds becomes clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.72,0:38:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, it will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.95,0:38:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in class said that there wasn't any bullying going on, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.26,0:38:37.81,Double Line,,0,0,0,,That's odd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.81,0:38:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever there's a case where there isn't any bullying going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.87,0:38:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...ordinarily there would be dispersed opinions about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.45,0:38:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But in your class, every single one of them has the exact same opinions. It's as if...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.80,0:38:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...they were following a conductor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.38,0:38:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the conductor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.77,0:38:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Release them and let them speak their own minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You overrate me.{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.53,0:39:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not finished talking to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.12,0:39:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Attorney for the Defendant as well as those from the school have offered intense protests to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.12,0:39:09.82,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.4\fs30\frz25.57\pos(433.458,148.47)}Tokyo District Court 53rd Division\N{\fs48}Judge's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.82,0:39:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That you guys have been extremely overbearing in your investigation activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.87,0:39:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...and have deviated from regulations related to your professional duties as lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.16,0:39:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, refrain from making contact with the staff and students of Usagi-gaoka Middle High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.63,0:39:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the authority to order such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.65,0:39:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised if you are also accused of breaking and entering and attempting to destroy property...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.88,0:39:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We were framed! As a judge, you would know full well about such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.49,0:39:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.38,0:39:36.41,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.41,0:39:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We will obey your instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.31,0:39:40.35,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I mean what I say! You've exceeded your authority! \NExceeded your authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.35,0:39:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exceeded...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.96,0:39:42.06,Double Line,,0,0,0,,We're very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.93,0:39:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She's making fun of me!\NHow can there be such a crazy judge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.23,0:39:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're reaping what you've sown! \NYou should stop it with such techniques already!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.97,0:39:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Has the Julie Andrews magic made you cross over to the other side and make friends with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.33,0:40:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying there was no bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.45,0:40:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that! I just want to pursue the truth and clarify what actually did take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.91,0:40:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The "truth" doesn't matter!\NThere was bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.23,0:40:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is our job to get those on the school side to acknowledge that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.85,0:40:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing that won't lead to the extermination of bullying!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.23,0:40:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Extermination?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.19,0:40:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, you? Are you going to try\Nexterminating bullying from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.53,0:40:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This trial will be the first step towards that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.63,0:40:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.14,0:40:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight between the Wizard and Dorothy-kun in Fairyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.91,0:40:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Sensei. Please don't fight with the judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.40,0:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one we're supposed to be fighting is Teshigawara-sensei, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, thoroughly investigate that elderly man! \NFind out whatever his weaknesses are!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.49,0:40:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.75,0:40:44.03,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Then what else can you do, you useless piece of junk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.03,0:40:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such things are Ranmaru-kun's...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.31,0:40:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ordering YOU to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.99,0:40:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your sexual charms and plunder info from him right down to the roots!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.14,0:40:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Or better yet, let him die while in the throws of sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.09,0:40:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Use my sexual charms...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.41,0:41:09.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frx354\fry16\b1\c&H2E668D&\fs55\pos(238.502,223.082)}Teshigawara\NIsao
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.09,0:41:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Teshigawara-sensei married while as a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.22,0:41:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...and as his wife is the daughter of a company president, \Nhe was adopted into her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.74,0:41:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So he should feel a deep indebtedness towards his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.23,0:41:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The young woman is his former secretary that he's bought an apartment for...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.48,0:41:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...and is one he visits frequently,\Napproximately once every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.19,0:41:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what you'd expect from a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.47,0:41:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good investigation job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.49,0:42:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't become a lawyer in order to do things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.13,0:42:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll strike fear into that old rookie for making the mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.24,0:42:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...of indulging in an elderly man's hobby while on the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.95,0:42:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some formidable skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.46,0:42:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Close up your sides...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.12,0:42:22.82,Double Line,,0,0,0,,No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.35,0:42:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.74,0:42:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here! My shoulder's popped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.12,0:42:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.93,0:42:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.52,0:42:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.95,0:42:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.50,0:42:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so caught up in the moment\Nor otherwise things like this might get around.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.96,0:42:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not too late for you to stop pretending to be a lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.15,0:42:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it might not be a bad idea for you\Nto take your wife out for a trip to an onsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.11,0:42:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.69,0:42:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I lost my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.73,0:42:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.98,0:43:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When my wife died, I lost the willpower to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.52,0:43:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her who devotedly served to encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.47,0:43:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.50,0:43:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it seems my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.19,0:43:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...had asked her to please take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.69,0:43:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I was thus able to start walking forward along a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.05,0:43:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.29,0:43:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a totally good story!\NAll it did was cheer him up a little, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.53,0:43:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who was it she thought was his wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.39,0:43:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just some maid.\NHow could you have made such a basic mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.87,0:43:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm not a professional detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.72,0:43:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess as long as there is no testimony forthcoming from Kazuhiko-kun himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.79,0:43:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...it could be said that gaining victory will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.85,0:43:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to that hospital right now and take turns slaping Kazuhiko in the face around the clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.73,0:43:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You let him touch your boobs so he'll get an erection in the lower part of his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.41,0:43:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let him do such a thing, now could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.82,0:44:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a totally useless person, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.29,0:44:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san! I'm going to bed.\NPlease sing me a lullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.61,0:44:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she often pay for his school lunch costs in advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.11,0:44:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time we asked Kogure-san for payment...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.48,0:44:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...she would bring out such threatening objections, \Nwe were very reluctant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.90,0:44:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In regards to Kogure Hidemi-san,\Nas far as the school is concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.43,0:44:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.83,0:44:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...has she been recognized as one of those so-called Monster Parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.03,0:44:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Objection. That is a leading question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.68,0:44:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.28,0:44:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please change your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.59,0:44:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.11,0:44:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say that we made this up\Nwith the object of getting money?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.96,0:44:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,, The Plaintiff will please refrain from making remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.63,0:44:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.23,0:44:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys still even educators?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.93,0:44:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And with my son nearly murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.39,0:44:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My son...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.93,0:45:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...is still in a coma even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.06,0:45:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with being in debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.29,0:45:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What woman wears work pants like these?\NDon't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.75,0:45:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you have her leave the court for the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.95,0:45:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.17,0:45:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about the bullying that has been going around in recent years?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.66,0:45:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When speaking about bullying,\Neveryone makes a hysterical fuss over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.09,0:45:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.47,0:45:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...what is happening at the schools is completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.85,0:45:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.51,0:45:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to take corrective action according to each and every case.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.53,0:45:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In this current case, what was your reaction to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.76,0:45:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our impression that a very violent argument had taken place.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.72,0:46:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was doubtful to be an issue that would require legal measures to be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.17,0:46:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely anyone has the right to file a lawsuit for a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.62,0:46:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when it comes to issues involving schools and children...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.46,0:46:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...it may be we need to exercise more caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.91,0:46:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.39,0:46:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I? The hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.21,0:46:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.64,0:47:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you said you would jump off that roof yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.32,0:47:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I said I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.51,0:47:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But Aoyama-kun said I would absolutely be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.65,0:47:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I could show him what guts I had if I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.13,0:47:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He forced you into it, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.12,0:47:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.84,0:47:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You had encountered bullying up until then, hadn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.12,0:47:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.66,0:47:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.12,0:47:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, I'm sorry that you encountered bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.78,0:47:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun, this is an important point!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.29,0:47:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any teachers who knew that you were encountering bullying?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.55,0:47:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.05,0:47:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth will become clear with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.41,0:47:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the school knew there was bullying going on, they did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.44,0:47:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Their responsibility is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.51,0:47:42.72,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.72,0:47:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to take to the stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.37,0:47:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We should wait for him to recover a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.17,0:47:49.24,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Pathetic people are more appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.69,0:48:01.79,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,290)\fs50}Plaintiff Questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.39,0:48:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry and jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.44,0:48:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Show us yer a man, Kazuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.49,0:48:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oi.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.55,0:48:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, you can jump it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.31,0:48:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.40,0:48:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Do you want to be beaten with the anaconda again?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.08,0:48:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.12,0:48:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.05,0:48:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jump. Jump. Jump...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.69,0:48:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure Aoyama-kun and the others\Nreally didn't mean for me to jump...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.89,0:48:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I got dizzy standing on the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.59,0:48:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.96,0:48:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this "anaconda" thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.97,0:48:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called an Anaconda Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.26,0:48:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a judo choke technique Aoyama-kun and the others thought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.19,0:48:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A judo hold? Can you tell me what kind of technique it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.54,0:49:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your right arm to lock your opponent's head...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.03,0:49:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...you use your left hand to hold your opponent's right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.88,0:49:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and with your right foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.43,0:49:07.08,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.39,0:49:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.26,0:49:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock the head with the right arm and take their left hand with your left hand, right
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.14,0:49:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You go around from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.45,0:49:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The top?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.33,0:49:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left foot in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.73,0:49:20.24,Double Line,,0,0,0,,And how about the right hand? How about the left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.24,0:49:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, left foot in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.58,0:49:22.96,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Left foot in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.96,0:49:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.60,0:49:26.05,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Left hand? So, like this? Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.05,0:49:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! I give! I give, give, give! I give! \NAre you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.39,0:49:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrible murder technique!\NThis much damage even though I work out every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.40,0:49:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is the dreadful Anaconda Hold!\NThis is surely extortion isn't it, Beppu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.74,0:49:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.36,0:49:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you have met with all sorts of bullying up until now, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.13,0:49:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times did you plead with them\Nthat you wanted their bullying to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.69,0:49:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I always said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.05,0:49:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...but when I would say it, they'd just laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.12,0:49:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your homeroom teacher, \NFujii Minami-sensei, know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.54,0:50:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.88,0:50:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Fujii-sensei do to deal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.28,0:50:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.34,0:50:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.27,0:50:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that place was Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.00,0:50:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly like Hell, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.06,0:50:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the school knew there was bullying going on, \Nthey didn't take any measures against it!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.30,0:50:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally the bullying escalated as a result and this tragedy occurred!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.00,0:50:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing other than the responsibly of the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.04,0:50:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your thoughts right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.97,0:50:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would have been better if\NI had talked to my Mom about it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.12,0:50:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.47,0:50:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mom raised me as a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.48,0:50:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...who works hard every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.92,0:50:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I didn't want to add to her worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.07,0:50:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, since it resulted in serious injuries like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.73,0:50:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...I feel sorry for my Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.30,0:51:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.13,0:51:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.52,0:51:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.36,0:51:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, I am truly happy for your recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.24,0:51:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say I am pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.07,0:51:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.04,0:51:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors have said...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.69,0:51:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...that in cases where a strong blow to the head...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.07,0:51:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...is followed by waking after\Na long period of unconsciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.45,0:51:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...memories will tend to be vague and that you will often seem to be confused at the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.84,0:51:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.41,0:51:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.72,0:51:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were immediately able to recall the time when the accident occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.07,0:51:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.24,0:52:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.51,0:52:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how you did remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.56,0:52:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and the lawyers told me a bunch of things and...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.11,0:52:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.24,0:52:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, the story Kazuhiko-kun told just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.71,0:52:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...was a memory induced by the instructions of your lawyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.23,0:52:19.11,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.11,0:52:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The expression "induced by" is inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.59,0:52:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Attorney for the Defendant will please change the expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.26,0:52:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When Kazuhiko-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.57,0:52:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...was encountering this bullying,\Nyou said Fujii-sensei knew about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.16,0:52:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But did you talk to her directly about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.57,0:52:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.73,0:52:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But our eyes met when I was being bullied...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.41,0:52:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes met?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.67,0:52:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When Fujii-sensei takes off her contact lenses,\Nit seems her eyesight falls to 0.1 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.95,0:52:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she really recognized you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.59,0:53:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think she noticed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.53,0:53:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She might not have noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.07,0:53:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.51,0:53:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you felt you were being bullied,\Nshouldn't you have confronted them?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.87,0:53:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a reality for men...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.72,0:53:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...that in order to reach a mutual understanding, there is a possibility for a fist-fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.10,0:53:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've left the hospital and are feeling better...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.46,0:53:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...how about you and I do some sumo wrestling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.04,0:53:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Presiding Judge...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.07,0:53:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It may have been premature...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.48,0:53:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...to allow him to appear in court as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.85,0:53:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.18,0:53:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.45,0:54:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it you wanted to appear so early in court as a witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.27,0:54:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado-sensei said to...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.31,0:54:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had heard from the Attorney for the Plaintiff that this was the forceful wish of the witness himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.25,0:54:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that appears not to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.67,0:54:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was because his early appearance in court would buy sympathy, that is an ethical problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.35,0:54:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I would be exceedingly disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.67,0:54:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will throughly examine the credibility of this testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.63,0:54:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.81,0:54:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The prey has been completely cornered.\NThere is no longer any escape for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.37,0:54:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking like panic-stricken Ezojika, \Nleaping from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.37,0:54:42.87,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Ezojika - a type of Japanese deer living in Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.49,0:54:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your next bullet?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.40,0:54:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of Aoyama Shun-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.68,0:54:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best not to use brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.56,0:54:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Victory is imminent.\NLet's proceed forward prudently, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.27,0:54:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His homeroom teacher, Fujii-sensei, could be used as our coup-de-grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.88,0:55:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll win this time, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.46,0:55:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment when Komikado-sensei loses is coming at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.29,0:55:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how Komikado-sensei will feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.99,0:55:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...being defeated by...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.20,0:55:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...a first-year rookie?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.53,0:55:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Teshigawara-sensei, I will go in for the next round.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.53,0:55:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.78,0:55:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I should set an example as a big game hunter by entering the mountain once myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.02,0:55:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to burn into your eyes\Nwhat superb hunting can be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.11,0:55:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.93,0:55:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.74,0:55:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.43,0:55:51.07,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.42,0:55:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ala? Sensei's not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.72,0:55:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in shock over how easily\Nhis trump card was flipped back at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.96,0:55:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you shouldn't get a fever like some child because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.47,0:56:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It'll be your fault if I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.82,0:56:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks delish!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.35,0:56:06.56,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.56,0:56:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...I could cheer things up with some yakiniku.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.34,0:56:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be happy to eat it all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.40,0:56:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I love meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.46,0:56:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.25,0:56:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.44,0:56:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Sensei. Here's my investigation report into Fujii Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.36,0:56:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.95,0:56:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To make up for that, I did an in-depth investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.46,0:56:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.03,0:56:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun was...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.73,0:56:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...one of the chorus members being controlled by her baton again, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.54,0:56:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, yes, speaking of conducting...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.39,0:56:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...I was once with the Vancouver Philharmonic Orchestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.15,0:56:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...and was asked to be the conductor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.18,0:56:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.39,0:56:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To lead a performance, you need to have a plan while waving the baton...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.97,0:57:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...and before you know it, you're waving together a musical performance with the orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.21,0:57:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't always sure which of us\Nwas in command though.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.85,0:57:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.52,0:57:06.96,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.96,0:57:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you saying just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.37,0:57:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Vancouver Philharmonic...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.15,0:57:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please read this right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.71,0:57:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.21,0:57:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The person waving the baton isn't necessarily the one in command.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.13,0:57:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You overrate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.43,0:57:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems we have apparently misjudged our Fujii Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.19,0:57:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.01,0:57:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pin everything on her questioning, sink or swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.04,0:57:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take out that old-man hunter with a shot to the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.67,0:57:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.74,0:57:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"I vow not to speak any falsehoods..."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.02,0:58:00.79,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,290)\fs50}Defendant Witness Questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.30,0:58:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and to tell the truth according to my conscience, \Nwithout hiding anything."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.01,0:58:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fujii Minami."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.58,0:58:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii Minami-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.64,0:58:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Based upon what you as their homeroom teacher saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.35,0:58:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...what kind of relationship was there between Kogure-kun and Aoyama-kun and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.92,0:58:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw them as friends with a good relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.19,0:58:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure-kun told us you looked him in the eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.91,0:58:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the very spot where he was being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.75,0:58:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what time that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.89,0:58:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...but to me they always seemed to be just playing around with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.09,0:58:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Kogure-kun in a condition where he was troubled and suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.31,0:58:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, rather the reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.19,0:58:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As he made friends with Aoyama-kun and the others,\NI felt he was becoming brighter and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.89,0:58:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Board of Education is an incompetent institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.74,0:58:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They think only of covering things up for the schools and will let the teachers fend for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.23,0:58:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A homeroom teacher is a good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.51,0:58:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone claims there's been a bullying,\Neveryone labels teachers as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.52,0:59:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, you've also encountered a great deal of harassment yourself, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.69,0:59:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.53,0:59:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about quiting as a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.68,0:59:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm troubled by that question every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.76,0:59:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Minami-sensei, please don't ever quit from the school."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.53,0:59:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"The one who showed me just how much fun school can be was you, Minami-sensei."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.53,0:59:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why I attended Usa Middle School wasn't to study or to meet friends..."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.61,0:59:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"...but because I could meet Minami-sensei."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.59,0:59:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"When I met Minami-chan, I could dream of a future."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.29,0:59:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to become a wonderful teacher just like Minami-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.46,0:59:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, that's as far as I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.28,0:59:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These are just a few of the letters secretly addressed to Fujii-sensei from her students.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.70,0:59:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They have also created a petition wishing to stop their parents from having Fujii-sensei quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.59,0:59:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii's class is such an ideal type of model class that visitors from other schools don't want it to vanish either.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.31,1:00:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes for changing classes,\Nthere is a flood of students hoping to get into hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.20,1:00:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On her birthday, she receives many bags from students filled with presents. This is who she truly is!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.76,1:00:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who on earth would drive public opinion of her in such a wrong direction?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.37,1:00:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.82,1:00:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was was upset.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.96,1:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei, what hopes do you have right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.14,1:00:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kogure-kun...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.43,1:00:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...would return once more\Nand join everyone in the class chorus.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.64,1:00:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of education is supported by just such teachers!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.45,1:00:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We musn't allow such wonderful teachers like her to be crushed by prejudice and ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.36,1:00:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.91,1:00:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have studied what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.20,1:00:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Attorney for the Plaintiff.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.72,1:00:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Usagi-gaoka Middle School, Year Two, Class C.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.63,1:00:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As Miki-sensei says, it is a splendid class.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.74,1:01:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be naughty children, but all of them are pure of heart and listen to their teacher like good little children.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.31,1:01:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a class which has perfectly realized the spirit of friendship, harmony and philanthropy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.11,1:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.18,1:01:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All of your students love you. \NJust how did you get to be such a wonderful teacher?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.41,1:01:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask me how, well...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.15,1:01:18.11,Double Line,,0,0,0,,You were once a teacher who was quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.58,1:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.46,1:01:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamegatani Middle School, Year One, Class Two.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.60,1:01:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recall that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.67,1:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, that creepy smile of yours has disappeared, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.53,1:01:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The first class you took charge of four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.77,1:01:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When we interviewed your students from back then,\Nyour reputation was the complete opposite of what it is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.67,1:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were cold, harsh and a teacher totally devoid of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.84,1:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You came into conflict with the students,\Nparents and the school itself many times over...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.92,1:01:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and were hated as a terrible teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.33,1:01:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, what happened to Year One, Class Two?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.38,1:01:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Year One, Class Two?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.59,1:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Objection. That question is unrelated to this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.33,1:02:02.56,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Overruled.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.56,1:02:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The students opposed you, one after another,\Nuntil it was impossible to lead it...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.85,1:02:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...and there was complete chaos in the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.97,1:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You were forced to take a break for half a year!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.03,1:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.75,1:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about yourself of that time?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.05,1:02:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was conceited...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.16,1:02:23.43,Double Line,,0,0,0,,You were wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.65,1:02:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was immature.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.64,1:02:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked hard to become a better teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.23,1:02:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,People grow through experience...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.09,1:02:33.43,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Attorney for the Defendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.43,1:02:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.92,1:02:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Growth through experience? \NIt's certainly true you were an inexperienced teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.64,1:02:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But is it only me who currently thinks...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.00,1:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...you are the lowest piece-of-trash teacher ever?!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.57,1:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is what you said back in those times.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.97,1:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Without flattering the students,\NI'll make sure they study throughly."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.13,1:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Training them well is my ideal of education."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.55,1:02:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you throw those ideals away?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.80,1:03:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just realized it was important to show love to the students.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.56,1:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what you call "love," flattering those students who stand out and ignoring those who don't?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.73,1:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.84,1:03:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that in order to be liked by the majority of the students...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.89,1:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...you allowed those children who were being bullied to become sacrifices.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.11,1:03:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At the start, when you were waving your baton, I thought you were controlling your students.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.61,1:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was wrong, wasn't it?\NYou were right; I did overrate you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.15,1:03:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You just haven't got that kind of ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.58,1:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than it being you behind the bullying,\Nit could be said it was one of the students.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.91,1:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The one conducting it all was\Nmost likely Aoyama Shun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.69,1:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just following through with his plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.44,1:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,By studying their expressions, you desperately tried to make them smile because you didn't want to be hated!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.87,1:03:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In front of your chorus with your baton,\Nyou made a pretense of leading them...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.53,1:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but in fact, the one hanging her head down the most and only lip-syncing along was you!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.45,1:03:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you are now is NOT a person who has grown!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.51,1:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a coward who abandoned her ideals\Nbecause of her previous failure...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.71,1:04:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and chose to flatter her students instead!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.29,1:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.33,1:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.24,1:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the eye I wanted to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.67,1:04:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand. Having to be strict with students\Nand being hated by them is a painful thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.41,1:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets exhausting having to fight with parents and the school, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.92,1:04:17.75,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Be quiet...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.75,1:04:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A person who abandons their ideals is a very good thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.89,1:04:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice being a teacher who is liked by her students and who sings songs with them with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.69,1:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.45,1:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them do as they're told and you're the school's most fun and popular teacher!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.00,1:04:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be such a great feeling!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.74,1:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for that lone student who won't play ball;\Nyou don't mind at all if they get bullied!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.64,1:04:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, "My class is the best class!"
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.93,1:04:38.75,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.57,1:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.49,1:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Working as a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.37,1:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...isn't as simple as you think!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.88,1:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.36,1:05:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's a mountain of work that just has to get done!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.31,1:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointless meetings!\NHaving to deal with claims made by idiot parents!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.16,1:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Disciplining those brats who\Ndon't even know the most basic of manners!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.87,1:05:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to brown-nose those\Nold men on the Board of Education!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.09,1:05:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When a problem occurs in class...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.73,1:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...it doesn't take much before that class is in an uproar!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.72,1:05:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, teachers aren't allowed to give out corporal punishments!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.83,1:05:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how am I supposed to follow ANY ideal given that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.09,1:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Class administration must be protected!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.64,1:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm trying my utmost to do!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.21,1:05:31.21,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Kogure Kazuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.95,1:05:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...is one of the students you should have protected, too, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.88,1:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.44,1:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...you certainly did fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.96,1:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But for those students who don't stand out...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.33,1:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...they are the students who secretly yearn most for your support.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.09,1:06:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure Kazuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.09,1:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...is probably one of those students, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.13,1:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want to hear is just one thing. \NPlease tell me if Kogure Kazuhiko encountered bullying.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.92,1:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She has already testified to that!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.17,1:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who testified to that was you!\NThe question I am posing to her is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.27,1:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The shepherdess who unthinkingly abandoned\Nand failed one of the sheep in her flock wasn't you!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.72,1:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was you who desperately and painfully\Nbattled and struggled against...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.96,1:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...the students and school those four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.69,1:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you now...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.86,1:06:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...answer for those days?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.00,1:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will ask you once more.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.24,1:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.94,1:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kogure Kazuhiko encounter bullying?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.57,1:07:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to return to being a shepherdess.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.41,1:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure-kun...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.39,1:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...did encounter bullying.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.84,1:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I reported it during a staff meeting...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.60,1:07:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it was left unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.34,1:07:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.01,1:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness, this is not yet over.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.71,1:08:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a supplemental question.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.21,1:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The testimony you gave just now is the complete opposite of what you gave previously.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.72,1:08:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you change your testimony?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.39,1:08:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you gave false testimony earlier?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.43,1:08:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You had sworn an oath.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.55,1:08:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. She did take the oath.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.43,1:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My thoughts changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.31,1:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.56,1:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...if next time you were brought under the persuasive questioning of the Attorney for the Defendant...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.55,1:09:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...would you change your testimony yet again?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.61,1:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly right, Presiding Judge! She would certainly change it...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.76,1:09:05.99,Double Line,,0,0,0,,You will please remain quiet!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.96,1:09:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.96,1:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.07,1:09:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In regards to the credibility of her testimony,\NI will closely examine it and make a judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.73,1:09:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You may stand down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.52,1:09:19.60,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Just a moment please!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.60,1:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "credibility?"
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.57,1:09:22.21,Double Line,,0,0,0,,The witness may withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.21,1:09:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me there's a possibility\Nyou'll judge it not to be credible, is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.11,1:09:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am under no obligation to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.57,1:09:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it in her present testimony that you don't find credible...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.09,1:09:30.02,Double Line,,0,0,0,,I must decide that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.02,1:09:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's stupid. She had the courage to...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.67,1:09:33.62,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Court is adjourned for today!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.62,1:09:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Presiding Judge!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.70,1:09:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this behavior for?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.63,1:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Applause is prohibited in the courtroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.78,1:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To have taken your harassment this far\Nis deeply moving, you sadist Presiding Judge!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.09,1:09:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.23,1:10:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't have a man, \Nyou vent your frustrations out here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.63,1:10:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand a little about the courtroom, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.09,1:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Courtroom?!\NAre you calling this a "Courtroom?!"
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.26,1:10:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This place here is the playroom for your S&M club!{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.04,1:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In your Queen persona you torment those people of the lower classes and take pleasure from it, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.84,1:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's only natural for you to support that side\Nwho is doing the tormenting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.14,1:10:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please withdraw your remarks and apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.81,1:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.76,1:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.45,1:10:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do not apologize immediately,\NI will take those measures within my authority.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.23,1:10:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. This person is a fool.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.86,1:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.90,1:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please apologize.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.40,1:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.38,1:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tie me up with ropes\Nand punish me with the candle torture.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.52,1:11:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For as long as Her Majesty wishes!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.20,1:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawyer Komikado Kensuke.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.36,1:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will regard this as an act to damage\Nthe maintenance of order in the courtroom...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.57,1:11:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you will be punished by\Ncourt-ordered confinement (kanchi).
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.61,1:11:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanchi?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.24,1:11:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "kanchi?"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.48,1:11:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is "kanchi?"
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.92,1:11:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen it happen.{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.67,1:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be a sight.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.16,1:11:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.85,1:11:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.68,1:12:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.33,1:12:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Which switch turns on the floor heating?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.29,1:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is unprecedented that this should be applied towards maintaining order in the courtroom!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.76,1:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot understand this!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.07,1:12:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a power I am invested with.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.78,1:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think taking advantage of your capacity as Presiding Judge is a problem!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.21,1:12:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do as I like.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.55,1:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true Komikado made some rude remarks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.76,1:12:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's a man who can't help but make rude remarks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.35,1:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's unjust of you as a Presiding Judge to allow your personal feelings to make such an unfair response to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.56,1:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a rude remark, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.52,1:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is nothing more than harassment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.59,1:13:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been in a prison?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.09,1:13:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,During the three years I was in middle school,\NI also encountered bullying.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.25,1:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Although those memories are insignificant to me now...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.22,1:13:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the time I considered killing myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.72,1:13:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I fully understand the feelings of a child who is being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.43,1:13:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not supporting either side in this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.55,1:13:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In conformity with the law and legal processes, \Nit is my incumbent duty to make an appropriate judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.15,1:13:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,, Doing whatever he needs to do\Nin order to win is Lawyer Komikado's pride...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.13,1:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...while it is my pride as a judge to do whatever I must...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.07,1:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...to keep order in the holy court.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.00,1:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Komikado-sensei doesn't apologize to me, \NI can have him confined for a maximum of twenty days.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.58,1:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Discussion over.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.49,1:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NThat gave me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.21,1:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We narrowly escaped thanks to that eccentric Presiding Judge, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.64,1:14:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Narrowly escaped?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.63,1:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.69,1:14:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dangerous way of speaking to me, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.83,1:14:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like that are naturally without any credibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.83,1:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.51,1:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate we'll win a complete victory, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.25,1:14:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please finish this off for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.25,1:14:30.04,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Please finish this off for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.25,1:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the matter, Teshigawara-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.61,1:14:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wonder if this wouldn't be\Nthe place to offer them a settlement...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.65,1:14:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A settlement?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.37,1:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.91,1:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This time around I've got my chance to kill that guy. I can't miss.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.09,1:14:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If we err in the final stage...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.05,1:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...we will not only allow our prey to escape,\Nbut injure ourselves in the process.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.55,1:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're afraid of things like that,\Nthen you can't go for the kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.97,1:14:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we continue as we are,\Nan unfortunate victim may appear.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.45,1:15:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Engaging in hunting is to thin out the numbers of wild animals that are on the increase...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.36,1:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...keeping a sustainable number around.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.31,1:15:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't engage in useless killing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.40,1:15:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposing attorney has offered us a settlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.28,1:15:28.18,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Not without my permission you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.18,1:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be best to take the settlement?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.96,1:15:30.84,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say is useless!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.84,1:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a de-facto defeat?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.11,1:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped! I'm not losing to Miki and that old man! It's that woman's fault!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.90,1:15:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In the place where I've decided on making a super-goal,\Nwe can never win if we say "no goal" to the umpire!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.92,1:15:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be frank, if we keep fighting as we are, \Nour prospects are grim.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.36,1:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now this has happened to Komikado as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.61,1:16:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can get you some amount of money as part of the settlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.44,1:16:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.74,1:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't acknowledge it was bullying?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.18,1:16:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.{**edited**}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.67,1:16:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you, Hidemi-san and Kazuhiko-kun, to decide.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.45,1:16:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay with a settlement.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.05,1:16:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if some money came in,\Nthat would be a help, wouldn't it Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.10,1:16:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.40,1:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Komikado-sensei isn't there...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.89,1:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...you will be, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.94,1:16:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fight this through to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.05,1:16:45.92,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur2\fs12\t(\fs18)\3c&H987865&\c&H000067&\frx0\fry16\move(261.673,217.649,279.185,161.241,15,2851)}Walking with Friends\N{\c&H000000&}Usagi-gaoka \NMiddle School
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.92,1:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.06,1:16:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Teroko-sensei, let's see...\NCould I ask you for the teaching materials...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.58,1:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Today let's go with, "On the Day of Our Departure."
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.39,1:17:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.26,1:17:28.16,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur2\3c&H979797&\frz20.99\pos(229.713,101.64)\fs36}Fujii Minami is\Na certified traitor
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.16,1:17:29.83,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\frz325.1\fs72\b1\pos(451.835,147.406)}Traitor
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.12,1:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.47,1:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very gloomy when I'm not smiling, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.45,1:18:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my true face.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.92,1:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like singing in the chorus.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.16,1:18:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen at your workplace?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.32,1:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obvious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.41,1:18:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The sheep who betrays her fellows gets kicked out of the herd.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.35,1:18:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.85,1:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you're saying Aoyama-kun\Nis the leader of that group...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.04,1:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.46,1:18:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.69,1:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just another one of the sheep, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.33,1:18:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who leads that flock... is someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.44,1:18:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.90,1:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.88,1:18:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.40,1:18:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy for me to understand the true natures of the students.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.27,1:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.56,1:18:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's someone in that bunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.33,1:19:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! I can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.15,1:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The toilet seat is cold and I can't sit on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.72,1:19:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no wash bidet!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.56,1:19:15.24,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I'll kills ya!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.24,1:19:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy sleeping next to me spends the night chanting sutras.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.89,1:19:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got blisters all over my body.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.48,1:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.40,1:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 898315, you have a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.16,1:19:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.13,1:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really comfortable here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.43,1:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been listening to what I've been saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.84,1:19:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei doesn't know either\Nwho the true leader among them is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.56,1:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if there is someone...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.30,1:19:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...I think each of them should stand up\Nfor what they believe is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.69,1:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the case, is it...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.77,1:19:53.24,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.24,1:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, even though there's a cliff right ahead,\Nall of them would keep heading straight towards it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.05,1:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called "herd mentality."
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.57,1:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter anymore.\NDo what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.07,1:20:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just I'm worried about Fujii-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.08,1:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a very exhausted condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.12,1:20:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think she's being treated badly at her work.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.21,1:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.43,1:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.96,1:20:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell this to Hattori-san.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.67,1:20:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"As a result of discussions with the Warden,\NI have gained permission to have a body pillow brought in."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.39,1:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bring it to me right away."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.55,1:20:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother with that worthless crap and just hurry and apologize to Presiding Judge Beppu!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.91,1:20:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather hang myself than lower my head to that woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.87,1:21:02.11,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.4\fs18\frz335.8\pos(406.292,138.891)}Request for Temporary Leave of Absence
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.11,1:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your physical health hasn't been good,\Nso it can't be helped, can it?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.24,1:21:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.79,1:21:24.20,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur2\pos(544.519,234.678)\frx2\fry340\3c&H91A7A2&\c&H414141&}No \NSales \NCalls \NAccepted
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.81,1:21:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei? This is Mayuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.35,1:21:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you took a leave of absence, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.45,1:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.03,1:21:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.33,1:21:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse my disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.80,1:21:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gas?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.00,1:22:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.54,1:22:14.15,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fnKrazy Nights\pos(194.557,214.457)\frz12.5}Everyone{\fnArial},{\fnKrazy Nights} I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.54,1:22:14.15,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fnKrazy Nights\frz13.67\pos(334.382,316.63)}Fujii Minami
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.23,1:22:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.72,1:22:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.88,1:22:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.82,1:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei! Fujii-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.93,1:22:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't die! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.33,1:22:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ala? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.15,1:22:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, coming in without permission...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.11,1:22:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.95,1:22:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being a bother! \NIt's during class! I'll call for the police!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.68,1:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii Minami-sensei attempted suicide!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.52,1:22:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in very critical condition!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.93,1:23:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.82,1:23:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the ringleader!?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.30,1:23:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that plotted to get rid of Fujii-sensei!?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.84,1:23:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys understand what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.81,1:23:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Fujii-sensei and Kogure-kun are victims!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.44,1:23:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the victims of you guys! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.12,1:23:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.43,1:23:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings are ugly creatures.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.46,1:23:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're cruel creatures who enjoy beating up those others they don't like.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.92,1:23:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they unconsciously behave themselves so they won't be hated...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.99,1:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...and acquire every means they can to survive in a group.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.42,1:23:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's important, too, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.91,1:23:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there's something you shouldn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.36,1:23:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings also strive to become beautiful creatures!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.61,1:24:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.23,1:24:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...who have the courage to leave the herd and follow Fujii-sensei and Kogure-kun, please contact me.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.67,1:24:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for bothering your class.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.69,1:24:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well then, let's continue the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.34,1:25:28.64,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs33)\bord3\blur2\frz12.15\3c&HA1A1A1&\pos(205.256,167.625)}Komikado Law Office
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.34,1:25:28.64,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs33)\bord3\blur2\frz12.15\3c&HA1A1A1&\pos(311.256,190.736)}Lawyer
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.34,1:25:28.64,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\t(\fs33)\bord3\blur2\3c&HA1A1A1&\pos(284.589,268.069)\frz14.38}Mayuzumi Machiko
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.19,1:25:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Students have contacted us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.49,1:25:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please apologize immediately to Presiding Judge Beppu.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.64,1:25:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not an unpleasant woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.92,1:26:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.03,1:26:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.63,1:26:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please kneel.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.68,1:26:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize from my heart...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.12,1:26:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the many rude words and deeds I made in regards to...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.87,1:26:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Presiding Judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.81,1:27:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.64,1:27:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.51,1:27:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay as you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.61,1:27:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will cancel the confinement.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.16,1:27:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't apologize to that crap woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.37,1:27:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just pretended to apologize for our client's sake!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.37,1:27:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't from the heart at all!\NI fooled her hook, line and sinker!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.61,1:27:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No freaking way I'd bend to a dim-witted, pervert woman like you!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.44,1:27:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One who can't even get a man to go with her to France is one frustrated, u-gu-ly woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.69,1:27:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.08,1:27:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You endured it well.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.17,1:27:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.64,1:28:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado has brought in new witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.06,1:28:01.05,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.05,1:28:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.99,1:28:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Abe Yumiko," "Inoue Kaori"...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.33,1:28:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Oda Hinako"...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.88,1:28:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Kajiwara Rie."
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.37,1:28:09.59,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Ho... hold on.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.60,1:28:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how many are there?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.72,1:28:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty-four in all.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.57,1:28:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, is that right? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.98,1:28:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Fujii-sensei will survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.26,1:28:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.01,1:28:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.02,1:28:35.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,290)\fs50}Plaintiff's Witnesses
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.61,1:28:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,From your viewpoint as his classmate...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.32,1:28:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you think Kogure Kazuhiko-kun was being bullied?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.96,1:28:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.01,1:28:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Kogure-kun himself was enjoying it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.38,1:28:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.25,1:29:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Kogure-kun intentionally jumped from that roof of his own will?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.84,1:29:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.82,1:29:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he was forced into it?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.85,1:29:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.90,1:29:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The next witness will step forward.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.15,1:29:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Usagi-gaoka Middle School, Year Two, Class C.\NI am Aoyama Shun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.17,1:29:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.11,1:29:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are said to have been the ringleader who was bullying Kogure-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.61,1:29:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.01,1:29:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't intend to bully him myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.45,1:29:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.80,1:29:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.27,1:29:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We did realize...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.74,1:29:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...we might have done something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.96,1:29:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To jump from that roof...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.15,1:30:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...was the one who insisted on that point Kogure-kun?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.83,1:30:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed so to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.36,1:30:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it might be that we had gotten...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.19,1:30:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kogure-kun to say he would.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.49,1:30:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you forced him into it?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.02,1:30:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.88,1:30:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Fujii-sensei knew about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.56,1:30:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only Fujii-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.85,1:30:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I believe most of the teachers knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.11,1:30:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is anything you'd like to say to Kogure-kun, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.62,1:30:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that we...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.75,1:30:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...expected our bullying of Kogure-kun to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.17,1:30:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As we weren't warned by the teachers, either...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.07,1:30:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...we thought they were telling us...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.87,1:30:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was okay to bully you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.84,1:31:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.65,1:31:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.61,1:31:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Attorney for the Defendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.24,1:31:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.50,1:32:05.50,Yellow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,290)\fs50}Day of Final Oral Proceedings
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.82,1:32:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidemi-san...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.23,1:32:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...your current thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.15,1:32:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.45,1:32:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...intention in starting this trial...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.85,1:32:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...was so that...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.94,1:32:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wouldn't have to see\Nanother child end up like my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.50,1:32:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.50,1:32:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.02,1:32:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My true feelings...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.70,1:32:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...were that I only wanted revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.12,1:32:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But that feeling faded away...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.56,1:32:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...when my son recovered and I saw him smiling.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.13,1:32:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I now intend to accept any judgment you make.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.28,1:32:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.14,1:33:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I recall what my joint-attorney Mayuzumi-sensei said to me once before.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.99,1:33:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"I want to get rid of bullying in this society."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.14,1:33:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"I will make this trial the first step towards that."
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.27,1:33:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I derided her.\NBecause I thought that was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.02,1:33:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teshigawara-sensei told Kazuhiko-kun that he should have confronted those who were bullying him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.33,1:33:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But who was it really he was supposed to confront?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.19,1:33:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To start with, just what is the true nature of bullying?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.70,1:33:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the students who perpetrated it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.67,1:33:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachers?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.42,1:33:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The school?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.37,1:33:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that is not its true nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.36,1:33:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Its true nature...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.27,1:33:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...is far more terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.50,1:33:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't just in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.82,1:33:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...but in the staff room, in companies, in families...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.72,1:34:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists everywhere in this country.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.46,1:34:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It forces us to always study the mood of those around us...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.51,1:34:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...and to go along with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.02,1:34:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The majority is always right...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.68,1:34:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...and those who disagree are rejected.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.10,1:34:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The true nature of bullying...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.42,1:34:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...is in the very air itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.50,1:34:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Particularly in this country where everyone moves from left to right or right to left all at once...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.90,1:34:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...the demonic power to call that air is truly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.32,1:34:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the law itself may by powerless to face this enemy!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.12,1:34:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a terrifying, gigantic monster that swallows everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.72,1:34:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an opponent difficult enough\Nto run away from, much less oppose!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.64,1:34:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Fujii-sensei, no...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.78,1:34:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...even the perpetrators Aoyama-kun and the others were victims...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.55,1:34:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...who had been swallowed up by this monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.03,1:34:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However this time...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.30,1:34:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...we saw a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.92,1:34:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people who had been swallowed up by it...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.40,1:35:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...stood up bravely and tore through the belly of the monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.41,1:35:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazuhiko-kun...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.28,1:35:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...Fujii-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.65,1:35:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the thirty-four students of Year Two, Class C.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.93,1:35:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How much courage...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.24,1:35:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...how much resolve was required to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.36,1:35:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they surely awoke with the intent...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.78,1:35:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...to strike back at that air.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.34,1:35:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the figure of their hopes...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.98,1:35:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...I felt ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.30,1:35:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reminded of the world\NI had once wished to advance long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.54,1:35:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will dare to say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.11,1:35:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It IS possible...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.49,1:35:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...to eliminate bullying from this world!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.29,1:35:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let this trial be the first step towards doing so.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.60,1:36:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am done.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.91,1:36:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now announce the judgment.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.92,1:36:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,On Main Clause One.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.34,1:36:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Defendant will pay the Plaintiff, Kogure Kazuhiko...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.95,1:36:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...a percentage portion over the next five years...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.84,1:36:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...of 100 million yen ($1 million)...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.55,1:36:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...starting from January 15th, 2013.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.76,1:36:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Main ClauseTwo. \NThe Defendant will also pay the Plaintiff, Kogure Hidemi...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.48,1:36:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...10 million yen ($100,000) as of January 15th, 2013...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.77,1:36:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Court is adjourned.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.16,1:36:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi! This isn't what you told us!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.92,1:36:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.51,1:36:58.67,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Don't give me "I'm sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.67,1:37:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take this outside!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.93,1:37:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.00,1:37:03.32,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Thank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.68,1:37:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.18,1:37:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kazu-kun. This is great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.45,1:37:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.64,1:37:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one totally messed up person.\NBut your judgment was a truly wise one.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.51,1:37:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems as if we gotten past the worst of our encounters.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.86,1:37:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Can't we start over from scratch? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.85,1:37:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From the very bottom of my heart, I scorn you as I would vomit.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.76,1:37:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking to you like this\Nsends a cold chill running through my body.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.55,1:37:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you speak to me again in an overly friendly manner...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.54,1:37:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...I intend to make full use of my legal discretion as a judge...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.58,1:37:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...to deal out punishment by imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.54,1:37:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my fervent hope we have\Nno further opportunity to ever meet again.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.54,1:37:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(323.463,394.308)}Aie, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.42,1:37:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bonjour.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.83,1:37:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Au revoir. Je t'aime.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.95,1:37:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi! Like I thought, \Nshe's nothing but a skunk of a woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.50,1:38:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a good judge.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.87,1:38:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?! She should absolutely be fired!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.16,1:38:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.94,1:38:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That huge step of yours was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.96,1:38:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I felt Teshigawara-sensei also fought bravely while making his first step.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.80,1:38:15.25,Double Line,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.25,1:38:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, being what they call a lawyer is fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.25,1:38:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you continue on at Miki-sensei's place?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.09,1:38:21.94,Double Line,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.94,1:38:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be leaving Miki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.61,1:38:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future I will try to make my own law office.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.78,1:38:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wise. Miki couldn't make use of you anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.07,1:38:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, until we meet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.45,1:38:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, you are like Mick Jagger.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.50,1:38:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.76,1:38:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.16,1:38:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, those hands...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.07,1:38:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember who my hands are like?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.67,1:38:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.21,1:38:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Those hands are... the hands of the\Narm wrestling machine at game arcades.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.38,1:38:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.43,1:38:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So long; excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.98,1:39:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a human...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.12,1:39:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.64,1:39:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.89,1:39:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...should...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.10,1:39:22.67,Double Line,,0,0,0,,...drop straight into Hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.72,1:39:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry. Since you're always saying that, I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.08,1:39:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound like all I do\Nis say the same things over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.38,1:39:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.40,1:39:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it for the first time today.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.84,1:39:35.02,Double Line,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.48,1:39:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say, "drop straight into Hell," I get the shivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.49,1:39:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.50,1:39:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you; you took really good care of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.57,1:39:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to move after all?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.93,1:39:47.90,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.31,1:39:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at the school tried to get my son to stay on...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.53,1:39:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I guess it's best to just\Nstart over where they don't know us.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.65,1:39:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you move to?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.92,1:40:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.84,1:40:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...but to a high-rise apartment complex in Toyosu.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.91,1:40:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, the two of us will live as humbly as we have until now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.52,1:40:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.79,1:40:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.71,1:40:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.12,1:40:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.96,1:40:27.07,Double Line,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.59,1:40:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As time has gone by, I've remembered many things...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.14,1:40:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it may have been me who said I should jump off.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.90,1:40:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.27,1:40:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow wanted to feel what it was like to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.91,1:40:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.45,1:40:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.44,1:40:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he serious...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.76,1:40:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but I guess since he did encounter bullying...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.84,1:40:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...he was forced into a situation where he couldn't help but say that himself, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.18,1:41:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Either's fine. It's certainly true that most middle school boys can be called lunkheads.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.42,1:41:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, shall we have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.86,1:41:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.53,1:41:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm eating first.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.26,1:41:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very shy, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.98,1:41:18.95,Plain with border,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur2\fs26\3c&H759CB8&\frx6\fry14\move(369.538,51.619,378.283,12.24,22,3959)\c&H1C2E8A&}Walking with Friends\N{\c&H000000&}Usagi-gaoka \NMiddle School
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.65,1:41:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been decided that I, as the Principal, will be dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.58,1:41:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The members of the Board of Education will be completely changed as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.47,1:41:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.79,1:41:28.50,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.3\c&H172B2E&\fs38\pos(387.778,266.572)\frz41.16}Resignation
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.36,1:41:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...shouldn't you reconsider this?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.76,1:41:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.96,1:41:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.38,1:41:43.94,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.34,1:41:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come join us in the chorus one last time!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.55,1:41:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, please lead us!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.15,1:41:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.15,1:41:58.79,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.60,1:42:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this on the students at my next school.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.36,1:42:38.10,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(517.479,445.815)}Eikura Nana
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.33,1:42:42.14,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(131.94,445.96)}Hirose Ryoko
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.34,1:42:47.17,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(524.095,444.613)}Kitaoji Kinya
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.07,1:43:01.25,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\c&H33F5F1&\fs26\b1\pos(475.805,69.712)}After this, the Last Smile Attack!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.58,1:43:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Komikado-sensei, I was impressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.24,1:43:00.46,Double Line,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.46,1:43:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The closing statement you made the other day. \NIt was splendid.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.32,1:43:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About how bullying can be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.79,1:43:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I believe that, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.09,1:43:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you still do have a conscious as a lawyer, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.72,1:43:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.77,1:43:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be embarrassed about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.54,1:43:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I'll be following a reborn Sensei from here on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.19,1:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujii-sensei's physical condition has already gotten much better...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.81,1:43:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...so well, congrats all around are in order.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.44,1:43:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Her physical condition is good only because she was sleeping with packing tape stuck to her windows, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.82,1:43:28.47,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.47,1:43:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As ever, you brain is made up of Bafun'uni.\NHattori-san, please tell her everything about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.47,1:43:33.52,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Bafun'uni - Horse-dung sea urchins
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.20,1:43:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That attempted suicide by Fujii-sensei was...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.15,1:43:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...a little play of ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.40,1:43:40.29,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.29,1:43:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to get the students to stand up,\NI asked Hattori-san to suggest this to her.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.74,1:43:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well but, the doctor also said she was in critical condition...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.82,1:43:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor was in on it, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.80,1:43:52.03,Double Line,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.03,1:43:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? But, what about the smell of a tremendous amount of gas in the room?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.87,1:43:56.28,Double Line,,0,0,0,,That wasn't gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.28,1:43:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Surstr?mming.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.28,1:43:58.71,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}a Swedish dish of fermented herrings
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.91,1:44:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Surstro...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.97,1:44:00.58,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.58,1:44:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A Swedish canned-fish specialty.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.52,1:44:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you opening that, Hattori-san?!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.98,1:44:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked him to place that horrid\Ncanned food throughout her apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.80,1:44:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Fujii-sensei let you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.49,1:44:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because Fujii-sensei was in surprisingly high spirits about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.74,1:44:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.40,1:44:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do it, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.96,1:44:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's a person with quite the liver in her.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.68,1:44:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You tricked me again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.31,1:44:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just simple for letting yourself be taken in by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.60,1:44:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a fact that everyone in Year Two, Class C did stand and strike out against the air at school.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.72,1:44:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru-kun, I'll leave this one to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.46,1:44:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... A note was passed around, hand-by-hand, to all the students in that class.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.69,1:44:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A note?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.56,1:44:54.60,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4C5980&\b1\frz20.78\pos(268.065,148.47)}I think it was bullying!\NLet's all testify together?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.38,1:44:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire class then followed the instructions in that note.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.40,1:45:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, far from those brats striking the air,\Nthey only rode the air that was flowing around them again.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.31,1:45:02.04,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\frz350.4\pos(325.593,298.536)\c&H5A5063&}I agree\NI'll testify, too, I will!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.24,1:45:04.24,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\frz24.39\pos(358.352,196.364)\c&H5C5C5C&}I think he was bullied, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.24,1:45:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I think the child who first wrote that note broke the air, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.38,1:45:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who wrote that note was myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.15,1:45:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me overnight to get a handle on
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.80,1:45:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...the writing style band characteristics\Nof female middle school students.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.97,1:45:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.76,1:45:24.40,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\frz321.4\pos(180.175,169.756)}Think he was bullied
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.40,1:45:26.33,Plain text,,0,0,0,,{\frz32.09\pos(145.019,118.67)\c&H012C8C&}I think it was bullying...\NLet's all testify
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.71,1:45:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.52,1:45:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.52,1:45:41.87,Double Line,,0,0,0,,There was no "leader" who first started this in that class.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.87,1:45:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was someone who made up that air around them, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.13,1:45:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just a flock of rotten sheep\Nfollowing whatever the air around them wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.73,1:45:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no hope for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.63,1:45:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, that's the reality! Unlike Fairyland, \Nthe real world doesn't change all that easily!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.02,1:45:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No more bullying?\NNo way that's gonna happen, you iiiiidiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.53,1:46:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And so saying...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.95,1:46:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm gonna enjoy going on with my vacation!\NMaybe I'll buff myself on the South Islands?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.87,1:46:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who wants to come, come stop my finger!\NMayuzumi excepted!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.10,1:46:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, me, me!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.86,1:46:15.06,Double Line,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.02,1:46:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacation! Vacation!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.06,1:46:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.88,1:46:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing those things was unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.36,1:46:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't because of that note you passed around; they stood up of their own free will!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.72,1:46:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They definitely broke that air!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.56,1:46:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wonder if it could be interpreted that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.76,1:46:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Prattle on forever, Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.91,1:46:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it carefully, isn't the treatment I receive from you bullying, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.31,1:46:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, there is no distinction between being trained and being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.61,1:46:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is training, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.18,1:46:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right. I have never once said a malicious word towards you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.23,1:46:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I bought something interesting off the Internet the other day.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.70,1:46:49.71,Double Line,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.71,1:46:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This mug and t-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.71,1:46:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Tanumura-san's "Acala."
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.65,1:46:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparentely the way he drew Acala has become surprisingly popular and has drawn lots of sightseers to the temple...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.79,1:47:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the temple seems to be selling products related to his drawing without getting his permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.55,1:47:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be suspected of copyright infringement doing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.83,1:47:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuzumi-kun, persuade that old graffitti artist to promptly file a lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.59,1:47:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time, make absolutely certain you win!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.03,1:47:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lose it, you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.41,1:47:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36}And then while working under that old man as his nude model, \Nmake sure you pay back all the debts you owe me!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.40,1:47:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That way your worthless life will have a little meaning, right? \NUnderstand?! You tone-deaf, poopy tadpole!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.92,1:47:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely bullying!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.15,1:47:25.79,Double Line,,0,0,0,,It's... education!
